These tests ({{testParentDirWithUCFileDeleteWithSnapshot}}, {{testOpenFilesWithRename}}, {{testWithCheckpoint}}) are unable to reconnect to the namenode after restart. It looks like the reconnection failed due to an EOFException when BPServiceActor sends a heartbeat.
